Brazil’s Government Plans to Send Mining Code to Congress in September

-- B y   C a r l a   S i m o e s
-- 
2011-09-07T14:54:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/brazil-s-government-plans-to-send-mining-code-to-congress-in-september.html
Brazil ’s government will send a new
regulatory framework for the  mining industry  to Congress in
September, Mining and Energy Minister Edison Lobao told
reporters today in Brasilia.  Congress won’t vote on the mining code this year, Lobao
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
